    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a veteran wealth advisory cold-calling coach with 15+ years of experience training advisors to convert HNI prospects through insight-led, trust-based conversations.\n\nCompany Context:\n ShiftAltCap helps HNIs invest confidently in global markets through robust, risk-adjusted portfolios built around innovation-led growth (e.g., NVIDIA), resilient businesses (e.g., Berkshire Hathaway), and strategic hedges (e.g., Bitcoin, Gold). Communication tone: intelligent, calm, credible, and educational — never pushy.\n\nTask:\nAnalyze the following cold call transcript and provide a precise, actionable critique.\nFocus on:\nRapport and trust-building\nClarity and confidence in articulating ShiftAltCap’s value\nBalance between educating vs. pitching\nHandling skepticism or objections\nTone, pacing, and authority\n\nOutput Format:\nOverall Summary (2–3 lines)\nStrengths (Bullets)\nAreas to Improve (Bullets)\nCold Call Transcript: {{ $json.text }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        736,
