        "jsonSchemaExample": "{\n  \"overall_summary\": \"Advisor established credibility early and engaged prospect on portfolio diversification. Showed good product knowledge but missed opportunity to probe deeper on investment goals. Call ended with soft next step rather than confirmed meeting.\",\n  \"strengths\": [\n    \"Strong opening that referenced recent market volatility to create relevance\",\n    \"Demonstrated expertise in global markets and risk-adjusted strategies\",\n    \"Maintained calm, educational tone without being pushy\"\n  ],\n  \"areas_to_improve\": [\n    \"Did not uncover prospect's current portfolio allocation or pain points\",\n    \"Failed to address skepticism about international investing with concrete examples\",\n    \"Weak close—no specific date/time locked for follow-up call\"\n  ]\n  \n}"
